sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Siswa
    participant View as Browser (Alpine.js)
    participant Ctrl as MisiController
    participant DB as Database & Models

    rect rgb(30, 41, 59)
    note right of Siswa: FASE 1: AMBIL DATA (SERVER)
    Siswa->>View: Buka halaman misi
    View->>Ctrl: GET /misi/{id}
    Ctrl->>DB: Ambil struktur Step & Hotspot
    Ctrl-->>View: Kirim data JSON ke Alpine.js
    end

    rect rgb(15, 23, 42)
    note right of Siswa: FASE 2: SIMULASI LOKAL (CLIENT)
    loop Selama Misi Berlangsung
        Siswa->>View: Klik pada gambar simulasi
        alt Klik Benar
            View->>View: Simpan progres & Tampilkan feedback
        else Klik Salah
            View->>View: Attempts + 1 (Potong XP jika > 3 kali)
            View-->>Siswa: Animasi Shake & Update Skor UI
        end
        opt Ganti Step
            Siswa->>View: Klik "Lanjut" ke gambar berikutnya
        end
    end
    end

    rect rgb(30, 41, 59)
    note right of Siswa: FASE 3: SIMPAN HASIL (AJAX)
    Siswa->>View: Klik "Selesaikan Misi"
    View->>Ctrl: POST total attempts ke Server
    note over Ctrl: Skor = MaxXP - Penalti (5% per error > 3)
    Ctrl->>DB: Update Skor & Sinkronkan XP Global
    Ctrl-->>View: JSON Sukses & Redirect
    View-->>Siswa: Misi Selesai!
    end